channel.title: Cant connect to server? error game js5connect
channel.description:
hey guys i have a 562 source and client, i use to able to do these kind of things with rsps but its been like 2 years and i totally forgot how to do this stuff and need to re-learn them.. -.-
So i changed the source's jdk to my version and compiled it and it works fine, but my client wont load up it gives me the "Error_game_js5connect" error and i have no clue how to fix it, originally i thought i had to go into the client's "build" and "run" and edit into my version of jdk but it gave me the same problem...
Any thoughts?
